Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,800)\pos(210,66.5)\fs31\bord0\fsp2}星之海原
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏又遇上雷雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就很难找到信号微弱的求救信号了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎儿 他们两个一定会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这么大的雨 搜救会很困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小班 别说些多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是连救援的人也遇到危险的话 只会徒增麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我冷静 骑士团已经前往救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也是有优点的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很让人意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给我们 所有人都回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果骑士团已经出动了 那就没有我们能做的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服从教官的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也一样 听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在这里等他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真不走运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨这么大 救援队也来不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雨要是能在天黑前停下来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还有卡路儿跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3-5和3-6区域已搜索完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的区域由于暴风雨而延后搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急降落到水上的话 就要在海上过夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能坚持住就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎儿 你真的打算一直留在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我们也在这里陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生也是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在这里等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们两个一定能平安归来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从那时起就一直在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上的事我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「风之革命」之后 某天我们家里突然来了个陌生男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们新的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从今天开始就住在我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他名字叫卡路儿·阿巴斯 是你们的干弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真棒 是弟弟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口渴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫诺儿 16岁 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我姐姐就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫曼纽尔 12岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个可爱的弟弟真高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移开视线了 真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 太可爱了 他在害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎你也来自我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喏 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是艾黎儿 今年九岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 艾黎儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不开心的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 还没问他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路儿你几岁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和艾黎同岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔 你的生日呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6月6日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的哥哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是6月7日出生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们才总是妹妹弟弟的争个不停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他为什么到艾黎儿家去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亲戚之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的父母过世了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲不忍心 就把他带回我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路儿也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卡路一开始什么都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔 这叫拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃 尝尝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 肚子不饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是连话都不回 真是太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我才是你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比你乖多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没精神也能吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人跟我讲话 我也会回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 艾黎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路是因为突然间被带到了一个不熟悉的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才这么紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 是紧张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 这也算哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是婴儿至少也会知道回应嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对突然到来的外人 我一时难以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 该睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐们还要准备明天的早饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妈妈在我刚出世的时候就过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也十分理解没有母亲时的寂寞心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和卡路虽然不是亲兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在一起长大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路和克莉亚一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是两个人单独相处 卡路他不会觉得不知所措吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能告诉大家 卡路真正的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 我们必须得把便当给爸爸送去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 艾黎儿 你也要去看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广场上正在上演「风之革命」的戏剧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜大人 请您原谅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您一定原谅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今才知求饶 真是难看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝葛列国里欧 皇后玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们穷奢极欲的时候 民众却生活在水深火热之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你毁掉了国家 该死的魔女 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 达米安 你也住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向母后道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母后？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路儿…就是王子 卡尔·拉·伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橡皮艇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,积水了 得把橡皮艇翻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗 我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡路儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一会儿 就会干了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉亚 用这个钓鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再三道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我有生以来第一次钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我钓过几次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和艾黎 诺儿 曼纽尔一起钓的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 是姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎儿有两个姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着夕阳 就会回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次飞上蓝天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸是飞机维修员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我们去给他送便当
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过半路上 我跟镇上的坏孩子打了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 爸爸 午饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经傍晚了 你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班头 麻烦 试飞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一直都能飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐到后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起飞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当前高度 300米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高度 500米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高度 800米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1200
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1800
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢高的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 高度2000
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边就是亚历山大城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 是海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道海的对岸 都有些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想亲眼见识下 「天空的尽头」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天空的尽头」…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就替我去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刻 我下定决心 一定要成为飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 跟你聊这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼 不上钩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼现钓现吃是很美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎处理之后 会做成各种料理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的能耐只在料理上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴恶毒 动不动就打人 罗圈腿 睡相差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事 艾黎是个很出色的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 艾黎很在乎卡路儿你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！你是这么觉得的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎总是生我气 发我牢骚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了卡路儿你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎现在一定也很担心卡路儿你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去之后 要好好道歉 好好感谢她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才谢谢你 冲着想去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你是个会为同伴着想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太抬举我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩 天亮就会回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 什么都没钓到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉亚 要小睡一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会睡不着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就继续聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次说说克莉亚你的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉亚为什么会想成为飞行员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人不反对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是跟妈妈分开生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟弟弟也分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是路易斯提督让孤独的我登上了伊斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易斯提督？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 原来我们两个很像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「风之革命」之后 我也失去了亲生父母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤单一人的时候被现在的父亲收养了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我和艾黎儿也没有血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前一直在亚历山大生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候都不曾打理自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿巴斯家的人教我了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是稍微睡一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在「风之革命」中失去双亲 生活于亚历山大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候都不曾打理自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴雷特洛斯前皇太子 卡尔·拉·伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许偷偷混进伊斯拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后准备向妮娜·维恩特复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克莉亚 是骑士团的飞行编队 我们得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 果然两人都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎 抱歉 让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家这么操心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你又笨又马虎又不正紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害得克莉亚也跟你一起遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾黎儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害大家在这里留宿 快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快和大家道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害大家这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾黎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才对您去上飞行学校抱有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是打倒罪恶 扶助正义的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼唤风 驾驭风的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是妮娜·维恩特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是伊格纳修
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙上次只穿内裤 这次又只穿泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个胡闹的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能这样嚣张也只是现在了 内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:39.77,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs32}第五话 呼唤风的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:36.55,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}逃げる場所さえなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:42.81,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}窓から見上げてるだけで精一杯の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:49.80,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}あの日の僕にも君がくれたその言葉の意味すら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:54.50,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}まだ分かりはずもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:01:02.04,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}絶望という名の雲の端へ飛べた世界に住む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:09.92,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}僕らにいまとっても強い風が吹いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:15.31,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}一緒にどこまでも飛べる気がしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:20.52,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}初めて見つけた自由握り締めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:28.37,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}まだ何も知らずに浸れた僕の幼好きた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:35.71,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}青い青い空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:42.81,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}无处可逃 仅仅透过窗台仰望天空经已竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:49.80,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那天给予我的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:54.50,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}其真意依旧琢磨不透
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:01:02.04,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}飞越名为绝望的云端 栖身于希望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:09.92,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}逆着狂烈的疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:15.31,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}坚信着定能一同飞向天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:20.52,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}将初次获得的自由紧握手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:28.37,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}沉浸在年少时情有独钟的未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:35.71,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那片蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:18.63,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}愛の言葉じゃ そこに出せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:25.20,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}届かない想いが 吹き荒れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:31.15,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}その身体には 鎧は重すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:37.99,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}未完成の心の 鍵を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:47.21,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}戦うわけなど あるとするのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:50.29,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}1つだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:54.64,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}震えている
